content.rendered: The Technology Student Association is a national organization of students engaged in STEM (science, technology, engineering and mathematics) and business leadership through regional, state, and national competitions.  The Arkansas state competition is taking place from March 13-14, 2023 in Camp Couchdale, Hot Springs, Arkansas.  More information can be found here:  https://www.arkansastsa.org/  and https://www.arkansastsa.org/state-conference
